cc:Work.dc:title: Super Decorative Farmer Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: I really thought I was done with the Ornate Frames. But this one was too good to not synthesize. Mister Horse and Misses Cow look at the center of the page, waiting for your awesome text. The top is already divided off and ready for your title (original title was "the desert farmer" but that has been removed to let you title it anyway you want!) .. enjoy!
